    "body": "If I use the scenario of the #2404 in https://deploy-preview-2900--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/v2/dev-novel/?selectedStory=RangeSlider.default\r\n - initial search: no bounds\r\n - set min bound to 1500 (around): min bound = 1500\r\n - type I: query = I, min bound = 1500\r\n - type K: query = IK, min bound = 180\r\n - remove one character: query = I, min bound = 180\r\n\r\nWe can see that this does not solve #2404 ",
